{
  "chapter": {
    "children": [
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "1",
            "text": "This is what Yahweh says:"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "“For three sins of Moab,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "even for four,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "I will not turn away punishment,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "because he burned the bones"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "of the king of Edom to lime."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "2",
            "text": "I will send fire on Moab,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and it will devour the fortresses of Kerioth."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "Moab will die in an uproar,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "with shouting and the sound of the trumpet."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "3",
            "text": "I will destroy the judge in her,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and I will kill all the princes with him,”"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "says Yahweh."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "4",
            "text": "This is what Yahweh says:"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "“For three sins of Judah,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "even for four,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "I will not turn away punishment,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "because they rejected the law of Yahweh"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and did not keep his statutes."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "Their lies caused them to go astray,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "after which their fathers had also walked."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "5",
            "text": "I will send fire on Judah,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and it will devour the fortresses of Jerusalem.”"
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "6",
            "text": "This is what Yahweh says:"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "“For three sins of Israel,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "even for four,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "I will not turn away punishment,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "because they sold the innocent for silver"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and the needy for a pair of sandals."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "7",
            "text": "They trample on the heads of the poor as people trample on dust on the ground;"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "they push the oppressed away."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "A man and his father go in to the same girl"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and so profane my holy name."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "8",
            "text": "They lie down beside every altar on clothes taken as pledges,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and in the house of their God they drink the wine of those who were fined."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "9",
            "text": "Yet I destroyed the Amorite before them,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "whose height was like the height of cedars;"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "he was strong as the oaks."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "Yet I destroyed his fruit above"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and his roots below."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "10",
            "text": "Also, I brought you up out of the land of Egypt"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and led you forty years in the wilderness"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "to possess the land of the Amorites."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "11",
            "text": "I raised up prophets from among your sons"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and Nazirites from your young men."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "Is it not so,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "people of Israel?—"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "this is Yahweh’s declaration."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "12",
            "text": "But you persuaded the Nazirites to drink wine"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and commanded the prophets not to prophesy."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "13",
            "text": "Look, I will crush you"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "as a cart that is full of grain can crush someone."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "14",
            "text": "The swift will find no escape;"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "the strong will not add to his own strength;"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "neither will the mighty save himself."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "15",
            "text": "The archer will not stand;"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "the fast runner will not escape;"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "the horseman will not save himself."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "16",
            "text": "Even the bravest warriors"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "will flee naked in that day—"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "this is Yahweh’s declaration.”"
          }
        ],
        "tag": "m"
      }
    ],
    "num": 2
  },
